OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FThe rising temperatures have brought
OL,7,Fwith them an early arrival of the tree
OL,8,Fpollen season, as ITV News' Amy Lewis
OL,9,Fexplains
OL,11,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,12,FGlenton
OL,14,FBritish hay fever season is "starting
OL,15,Fearlier and lasting longer" due to
OL,16,Fclimate change, according to Hay Fever
OL,17,FUK, meaning that sufferers could be
OL,18,Ffeeling symptoms earlier in the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
