OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FDifferent types of pollen tend to peak
OL,7,Fin different seasons, and late
OL,8,FFebruary to early March falls in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the tree pollen season.
OL,11,FTree pollen levels are currently "very
OL,12,Fhigh" in London, according to
OL,13,FKleenex's pollen tracker, while levels
OL,14,Fare "high" in areas including
OL,15,FBirmingham, Brighton, Derby,
OL,16,FManchester, and Oxford.
OL,18,FITV News explains why 2026 could be a
OL,19,Fpollen-heavy year and how to manage
OL,20,Fhay fever symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
