OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FWhat is hay fever?
OL,8,FHay fever is a common allergy to
OL,9,Fpollen that can cause a number of
OL,10,Funpleasant symptoms for sufferers.
OL,12,FHay fever, also known as allergic
OL,13,Frhinitis, happens when the immune
OL,14,Fsystem overreacts to allergens in the
OL,15,Fair, and as well as pollen, it can be
OL,16,Ftriggered by house dust mites, mould
OL,17,Fspores and pet dander.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
