OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FMild winters, such as 2025`26, can
OL,7,Fextend the duration of certain pollen
OL,8,Fseasons, potentially worsening
OL,9,Fsymptoms for allergy sufferers.
OL,11,FTypically different types of pollen
OL,12,Fthrive in different seasons:
OL,14,FThe weather has also been warmer than
OL,15,Fusual this week, with the Met Office
OL,16,Frecording temperatures of 18.6C at Kew
OL,17,FGardens in London on Wednesday - the
OL,18,Fhighest February temperature since
OL,19,F2019.
