OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FThis typically makes hay fever worse
OL,7,Fas plants and trees release more
OL,8,Fpollen, and windy conditions will help
OL,9,Fit to spread further.
OL,11,FWill hay fever keep getting worse?
OL,13,FWarmer temperatures for longer periods
OL,14,Fdo lengthen pollen seasons, and with
OL,15,Fglobal temperatures on the rise, it's
OL,16,Flikely that pollen counts will also
OL,17,Fcontinue to increase.
OL,19,FWhat can you do if you've got hay
OL,20,Ffever?
