OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FThis includes the jab Kenalog, which
OL,7,Fis commonly advertised and sold
OL,8,Fonline, despite the fact that it is a
OL,9,Fprescription-only medication that has
OL,10,Fknown side-effects.
OL,12,FKenalog can cause increased blood
OL,13,Fpressure, dizziness, severe abdominal
OL,14,Fpain, depression and mood swings.
OL,16,FYou should speak to a pharmacist or
OL,17,Fyour GP if you are looking for ways to
OL,18,Fimprove your hay fever symptoms. They
OL,19,Fmay then advise you to take
OL,20,Fantihistamines or steroid nasal sprays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
